articles.author: Andy Greene
articles.title: Mark Knopfler Unites With Over 60 Guitar Gods for ‘We Are The Wold’-Style Charity Single - Rolling Stone
articles.description: "Going Home (Theme From Local Hero)” features Bruce Springsteen, David Gilmour, Eric Clapton, Slash, and Jeff Beck's final studio recording.
articles.content: Dire Straits’ Mark Knopfler has united with over 60 artists — including Bruce Springsteen, David Gilmour, Slash, Eric Clapton, Ringo Starr, Ronnie Wood, Jeff Beck, Pete Townshend, Sting, Brian May, J… [+2719 chars]
